rows.label: tlk45320651_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I heard a rumor that the inventor of
artificial Blades lived in Trigo,
so I went to pay him a visit.

rows.label: tlk45320651_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Unfortunately, I couldn't get him
to tell me any juicy secrets about
artificial Blades.

rows.label: tlk45320651_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I did get to see a bunch of the materials
used to make them, though.

rows.label: tlk45320651_03_msg0013
rows.name:
...That was as much as I got to see,
but I suspect the list goes on for
at least ten times that length.

rows.label: tlk45320651_03_msg0014
rows.name:
At any rate, I intend to visit Professor
Tatezo again in the near future. I'll get
those juicy secrets out of him yet!
